---
import CornellNote from '../../../components/CornellNote.astro';

// LaTeX constants
const limInf = "$\\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to \\infty}$";
const mathMain = "$\\sqrt{x^2 + 2x} - x$";
---

<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>유형 02. 무리식 (무한대) - 상세 연습</title>
		<!-- KaTeX -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css">
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js"></script>
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js"></script>
		<style>
			body {
				background-color: #e0e0e0;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 20px;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
			}
			/* [표준 디자인 시스템] 난이도 내비게이션 최적화 */
			.difficulty-container {
				margin-top: 50px;
				padding: 25px;
				background: #f9f9f9;
				border-radius: 16px;
				border: 1px solid #eee;
			}
			.difficulty-list {
				display: flex;
				gap: 12px;
			}
			.difficulty-btn {
				flex: 1;
				padding: 15px;
				text-align: center;
				border-radius: 12px;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: bold;
				font-size: 1.3rem;
				transition: transform 0.2s ease;
			}
			.difficulty-btn:active { transform: scale(0.95); }
			
			.btn-low { background: #eef7ee; color: #2e7d32; border: 1.5px solid #2e7d32; }
			.btn-mid { background: #ebf3ff; color: #1565c0; border: 1.5px solid #1565c0; }
			.btn-high { background: #fff8e1; color: #a0522d; border: 1.5px solid #a0522d; }

			@media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
				.difficulty-container { padding: 15px !important; }
				.difficulty-list { gap: 8px !important; }
				.difficulty-btn { 
					padding: 12px 5px !important; 
					font-size: 1.1rem !important; 
				}
				body { padding: 10px; }
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<CornellNote title="유형 02. 무리식" chapter="Chapter 01 Practice">
			
			<div slot="cues">
				<p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">💡 집중 공략 포인트</p>
				<ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6; color: #444;">
					<li>무리식이 포함된 { "$ \\infty - \\infty $" } 꼴 확인</li>
					<li>분자를 1로 보고 **유리화** 진행</li>
					<li>유리화 후 { "$ \\frac{\\infty}{\\infty} $" } 꼴로 변형하여 계수 비교</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<section>
				<div class="type-section">
					<h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1a1a1a; border-bottom: 2px solid royalblue; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 5px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
						[핵심 문제]
					</h4>
					<p>다음 극한값을 구하시오.</p>
					<div style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.6rem; margin: 40px 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.02); padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px;">
						<span class="math">{limInf} ({mathMain})</span>
					</div>
					
					<!-- Progressive Disclosure: Strategy -->
					<details style="margin-top: 30px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px; background: #fff;">
						<summary style="font-weight: bold; color: #1a73e8; cursor: pointer; padding: 5px;">💡 해결 전략 (클릭하여 확인)</summary>
						<div style="margin-top: 10px; padding: 10px; border-top: 1px dashed #eee; color: #444; line-height: 1.6;">
							이 문제는 { "$ \\infty - \\infty $" } 꼴입니다. 루트를 벗겨내기 위해 <b>분자의 유리화</b>를 시도해야 합니다. 분모에 { "$ 1 $" }이 있다고 생각하고 켤레식을 분모, 분자에 곱해 보세요.
						</div>
					</details>

					<!-- Progressive Disclosure: Step-by-Step Solution -->
					<details style="margin-top: 15px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px; background: #fff;">
						<summary style="font-weight: bold; color: #e63946; cursor: pointer; padding: 5px;">📝 단계별 풀이 (마지막에 열어보세요!)</summary>
						<div style="margin-top: 10px; padding: 10px; border-top: 1px dashed #eee; color: #444; line-height: 1.8;">
							<p><b>Step 1. 유리화 진행</b><br/>분모와 분자에 { "$ \\sqrt{x^2+2x} + x $" }를 곱합니다.<br/>
							{ "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to \\infty} \\frac{(\\sqrt{x^2+2x}-x)(\\sqrt{x^2+2x}+x)}{\\sqrt{x^2+2x}+x} = \\lim_{x \\to \\infty} \\frac{(x^2+2x) - x^2}{\\sqrt{x^2+2x}+x} $" }</p>
							
							<p><b>Step 2. 식 정리</b><br/>분자를 정리하면 { "$ 2x $" }가 남습니다.<br/>
							{ "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to \\infty} \\frac{2x}{\\sqrt{x^2+2x}+x} $" }</p>
							
							<p><b>Step 3. 최고차항 계수 비교</b><br/>분모의 최고차항은 { "$ \\sqrt{x^2} = x $" }와 { "$ x $" }이므로 합치면 { "$ 2x $" }급입니다.<br/>
							따라서 { "$ \\text{극한값} = \\frac{2}{1+1} = 1 $" } 입니다.</p>
						</div>
					</details>

					<!-- Difficulty Level Navigation -->
					<div class="difficulty-container">
						<p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #333; font-size: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
							🎯 내 실력에 맞는 문제 도전하기
						</p>
						<div class="difficulty-list">
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/levels/type02-low/" class="difficulty-btn btn-low">[하]</a>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/levels/type02-mid/" class="difficulty-btn btn-mid">[중]</a>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/levels/type02-high/" class="difficulty-btn btn-high">[수능]</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<a href="/wiki/chapter01/problems-inf/" class="back-link" style="margin-top: 40px; display: inline-block;">← 유형별 목록으로 돌아가기</a>
			</section>

			<div slot="summary">
				<p>무리식의 무한대 극한에서는 **'유리화'**가 선택이 아닌 필수입니다. 유리화만 하면 우리가 잘 아는 계수 비교 문제로 바뀐다는 점을 기억하세요!</p>
			</div>
		</CornellNote>

		<script is:inline>
			if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {
				document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
					if (typeof renderMathInElement === 'function') {
						renderMathInElement(document.body, {
							delimiters: [
								{left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true},
								{left: '$', right: '$', display: false}
							],
							throwOnError : false
						});
					}
				});
			}
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
